  	    "@type": "NewsArticle",
  	    "headline": "How to Soften Your Spiky Beard",
  	    "alternativeHeadline": "Because the last thing you want is a death trap on your jaw",
  	    "url": "http://gq.com/story/how-to-soften-your-beard",
  	    "image": ["http://media.gq.com/photos/561176c46349dcfa15f22ca6/master/pass/1006SP-gq-pricky-beard-maintenance-tout.jpg"],
